response.overview: The Tørrfluelandet series are the best-selling fishing films in the Nordics. Cozy and good humor in wild and beautiful nature! Follow the enthusiasts and Andreas in the hunt for 24-hour hatchlings and large trout. In underrated Salta, they meet the year's first rhodani hatching in mid-May. In Rævsjøen they are tricked by thousands of mayflies, and in the legendary False river, the aurivillia emerge from the river gravel in such large quantities that both the fish and the fishermen go off their hinges.
response.tagline: Dry fly fishing after trout in Norway, with a touch of comedy
response.title: Tørrfluelandet 2
